    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted on the basis of regulatory precedent: ASTM F1717 specifies a single test configuration and FDA guidance does not require multi-rate testing for static compression-bending submissions. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the intended regulatory use. Package accepted.",
